title: The Hooters Supply Chain
description:
The boys riff on the meanest thing someone could say to them, learn how  pigeons bang, and decide that leap years are stupid. They also hear from  a listener that got cheated on in an unexpected way.

Hear the full episode AND get an exclusive episode every Friday (+ instant access to 140 bonus episodes) for $5/month at https://www.patreon.com/stiffsockspod
